## Update: Inflection's Payment Processor is down

Since we can't pay Inflection at this time, both Inflection 3 Pi and Inflection 3 Productivity models will be down until further notice.

### Grok updates

xAI has asked us to rename Grok 2 to Grok Beta. requests to `x-ai/grok-2` will alias to `x-ai/grok-beta`.

The pricing of completions has increased to $15/M. But, good news, the context length is much longer, now 131,072!

### Liquid LFM updates
This week, Liquid LFM 40b will start to be priced at $1/M input, $2/M output. The `:free` variant will remain active.

ReginaGeorge: 

This is helpful information about updates to xAI's services:

**Grok:**

* The name "Grok 2" is changing to **Grok Beta**.
* Existing requests to `x-ai/grok-2` will automatically be redirected to `x-ai/grok-beta`.

**Liquid LFM:**

* The pricing for Liquid LFM 40b is changing. It will now cost:
    * $1 per 1 million input tokens
    * $2 per 1 million output tokens
* The `:free` variant of Liquid LFM will continue to be available at no cost.


These updates are useful for anyone who uses xAI's services. Developers and researchers should be aware of the name change for Grok and adjust their code accordingly. The pricing changes for Liquid LFM may also impact budgeting decisions.

## New Claude 3.5 Sonnet, new Llama Nitro provider <a:nitro_booster:1175038642142584862>

Plus, ICYMI, Mistral models, Grok context extension, and other updates!

### New Claude 3.5 Sonnet

Seems a lot better. Improvements across many benchmarks. No code changes needed to try it out! Their launch announcement is [here](https://www.anthropic.com/news/3-5-models-and-computer-use). (Tip: you can hover over the info icon next to providers to see when models are upgraded like this.) 

### Llama 3.1 405b Nitro

Powered by a temporarily-secret provider, check out these new super-fast (and pricey) endpoints. The 405b nitro is about 70% faster than the next fastest provider!
- https://openrouter.ai/meta-llama/llama-3.1-405b-instruct:nitro (~120 tps)
- https://openrouter.ai/meta-llama/llama-3.1-70b-instruct:nitro

### Ministral

- Ministral 8b is a fast (150 tps), high-context (128k) and powerful new model from Mistral, already ranking #4 for tech prompts. A cheaper and faster 3b is also available. https://openrouter.ai/mistralai/ministral-8b

## Other updates

- Grok 2 has been renamed to Grok Beta. requests to `x-ai/grok-2` will alias to `x-ai/grok-beta`. The context length has increased to 131,072, and output price to $15/m.

- As mentioned above, Liquid LFM 40b is now priced at $1/M input, $2/M output (the `:free` variant will remain active)
